{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"da57d59fe5","title":"对《希腊伦理思想的来源与发展线索》一文的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"25510ab31b","index":0,"year":1962,"month":9,"day":15,"articleId":"da57d59fe5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"2ce5287724","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"少奇，即刘少奇。"},{"id":"4871ffbc71","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"北京大学教授周辅成写的这篇文章刊登在1962年9月9日《文汇报》上。文章讲了以下四个问题：伦理学来源于阶级斗争；为奴隶制社会生活所决定的特点；围绕“中唐”“和谐”为中心的表现形式；争论的问题与派别。"},{"id":"7e677b641e","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈伯达，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央政治研究室主任、毛泽东的秘书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f155a561d4","type":"title","text":"对《希腊伦理思想的来源与发展线索》一文的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5"},{"id":"2ce5287724","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇\"同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5"},{"id":"4871ffbc71","type":"paragraph","text":"此文时可一阅，如你有时间和兴趣的话。阅后交陈伯达同志一阅。然后还我。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5"},{"id":"7e677b641e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5"},{"id":"9db8530e04","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5"},{"id":"a565a981f6","type":"paragraph","text":"听谓伦理学，或道德学，是社会科学的一个部门，是讨论社会各阶级客不相同的道德标准的，是阶级斗争的一种工具。其基本对象是论善恶（忠好、好坏）。统治阶级以为善者，被统治阶级必以为恶，反之亦然。就在我们的社会也是如此","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5"}],"page":{"id":"69a02b69a2","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"da57d59fe5","start":248,"end":248}}}},"__N_SSG":true}